PrecisSanctionning of BY-LAW NO. 44 adopted by THE CANADIAN MEDICAL PROTECTIVE ASSOCIATION on August 21, 1996, to amend its By-Law No. 39 by eliminating the appointed Councillors from Membership on the Council and taking away the vote of the Secretary-Treasurer and the Assistant Secretary-Treasurer.

Sanctionning of BY-LAW NO. 44 adopted by THE CANADIAN MEDICAL PROTECTIVE
